      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>gravy bread</strong> to the other side of the tray with the mustard & onion chicken</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 16-17 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the bread is crispy on the outside</p>",
